Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, no! What should I do? This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're so clumsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't just whine, help me pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, can someone please help me pick these up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gosh, they're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.43,0:00:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's this tiny idiot's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What's wrong, Aisaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.61,0:00:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga really loves Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She thinks she has to be good because Santa is always watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All girls love Christmas, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you two finding time to study for your exams with all these party preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, we've been studying as a group recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, Aisaka-san always has good grades,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and your grades are always good too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm worried about Haruta-kun, Haruta-kun and Haruta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, Haruta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And Haruta-kun too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.57,0:01:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruta-kun hasn't been helping with the preparations, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura ordered him to stay out of this so he could study.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Promise me you two won't let your grades drop, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm worried that you two might be spending too much time on the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Speaking of which, are you coming to the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How could I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't have any dates on Christmas Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.97,0:01:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but for the sake of my pride, I won't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really hope it's a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You guys are putting a lot of effort into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.66,0:01:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so you'll definitely reap the rewards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yo! Taiga-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, Minorin! Club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We spent the whole time working out in the gym!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda, hurry up or the coach will start complaining again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, we really haven't been talking much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The party will definitely be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin is being really weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think she'll definitely cheer up if she comes to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We have to do our best to make it an amazing party!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah! Let's do it, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So slow! What were you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We got held up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm in charge of the ornaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look, isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As expected of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stupid! Stupid! Go redo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:05:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, should you really be saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Weren't you trying to be good for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, what a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that for the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The P.E. teacher asked us to clean out the storeroom in return for letting us use the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, let me care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura, make the stars with Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here, scissors and glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go, Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't hold scissors like that, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hold them like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My, my, they sure are getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, let's go and help out over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? What? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:45.22,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, what are they trying to stir up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? Stir what up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't play dumb, you know I'm talking about Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:06:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh... liking Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lately it seems like everyone is trying to pair them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're really obsessed with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.09,0:06:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? Why would I be jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.43,0:06:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}get pissed off when outsiders spread stuff about someone else's love life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is how a father feels when his daughter is about to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wouldn't know. It's not like I have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also, I've never met my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Not allowing her to fall, get hurt, or cry."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Watching the most precious woman of your life get taken away from you by another man."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Not knowing if that man will treasure her as much as you do."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've never had those thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:07:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Surely it won't be fun for you to watch Yuusaku and Taiga date, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's like the total opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're not her father, but you treasure the woman you're determined not to lay a hand on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You already have another woman in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's like playing house. You three know exactly which characters you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Like pretending to be daddy, mommy and the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do you have to pretend to be daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your relationship with Taiga seems really unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think you should stop playing this childish game of house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You've been making mistakes all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why don't you wake up before you get hurt even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.08,0:07:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should forget everything and just start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you could also give me another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just pretend you didn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What was I even talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just forget everything I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After all, what you really don't understand is yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, put your pencils down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes! It's over! It's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:43.53,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:45.02,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haruta, you're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Quiet down and listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:47.52,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Christmas! Christmas is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's normal school tomorrow and the day after,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so don't get too excited about Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you want to have lunch with Ryuuji and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry, I have to go to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sadly, Minorin has club activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know, I heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm really sorry for turning you guys down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Well, it's nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It just seems like we haven't had a chance to talk lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I mean, Taiga and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, our Coach was taken over by the dark side, so now our practice is harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She ran away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was planning to create a chance for you guys to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After we had left and arrived at the shop, I'd be like "Sorry, I have something to do!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You even planned a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Angel Taiga sure is passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There {\i1}will{\i0} be another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go eat something before we go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I wasn't going to lie, I really have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.44,0:10:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After I go home to get something, I need to go to the post office.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuuji, you don't need{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're here, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, are you free right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I need to have a talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why don't you come and have lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay? Okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No... Sorry, I have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to go to the post office with her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait, Ryuuji! I said you didn't need to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait! Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why did you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Besides, what's with that gal girl pretending to be Kitamura's childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait, scratch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I meant, the honest girl, Kihara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right, it won't be a lie if I go to the post office with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:10:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? The thing you need to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you plan to take them all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't touch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These are none of your concern; just help me get the cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If it weren't Christmas, I would've beaten you up already,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but for the sake of being good, I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These are Christmas presents for {\i1}that{\i0} family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't tell me you're planning to give them another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not because of that, it's because it's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's because they're my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I also got presents for you and Ya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know what you want to say, but I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to get the cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I went to an all-girls Catholic school all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was rejected by the high school because of bad behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At that school, you have to do volunteer work with the sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hate to put it this way, but we play with orphans and do some other odd jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The present with "Santa" written on it is actually for those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}First, presents for {\i1}that{\i0} family, and now for orphans?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, but I don't understand you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to tell them that there are people who are watching over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Christmas is a chance to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Even if you don't have parents and don't believe in God...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if that's the case, there's someone watching over you."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's what I want to show them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want them to know that someone cares about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know. You're right. It's self-satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it's because I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}someone is actually watching over me somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To me, that person is Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Santa, Santa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you really believe in him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I truly love Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The streets, shops... Everywhere is glittering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It’s dazzling and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone looks really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The world is overflowing with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I feel like I'm part of that happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to be part of the happy, glittering scene on Christmas Eve...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}while wearing a happy face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really met Santa before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was on a Christmas Eve when my parents were still together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was sleeping under the Christmas tree in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I woke up because it was cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}then I looked out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Santa was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He gave me a present and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"If you be a good child, I'll definitely come again."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, it might have been a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But even so, it was a really happy dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I want to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you think I'm stupid for believing in a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whatever, it's not like its real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not like I'm clinging to something real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes! The Christmas tree is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This will be fabulous once we put it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think the party will be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuri-chan, are you going to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I said I'm not going for the sake of my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, yeah! I should buy a present for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Watches, bags, or even accessories!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll be a reward for thirty years of hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're thinking that I'm wasting money, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.17,0:15:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're thinking that I'm just a single woman who's falling for advertising tactics, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:37.82,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I shouldn't waste money because I need seventy million yen for retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But what if I stop myself from buying things,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}then I'm finally all "Yay! I have a hundred million yen!",
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but before I know it, inflation in Japan gets so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}that all the money I've saved becomes useless{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait, huh?! I just predicted the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Perhaps I should buy myself an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's here! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Check if we have all the parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't believe you managed to get something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was a decoration in a model show I was on, so I asked them if I could have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm amazing, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, you're a stupid Chihuahua, but you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the best tree ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No one could disagree!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll be even better once we put it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone, come on, let's get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are the supporting parts all right like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow! I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's the top part.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aisaka-san, you look pretty light,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so can you get on my back and put this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With the shoes I just went to the toilet with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Different people really do have different interests...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, please take them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you dozing off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come and help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-Sure, I think this is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, what was that for?! It was dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you doing, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:16:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But your reflexes are pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As expected from the Palmtop Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}But it's because I believe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}someone is actually watching over me somewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga, you're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Perhaps you didn't actually have someone watching over you for the past seventeen years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but it's different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You also have Yasuko, Inko-chan, and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tomorrow, Kushieda will definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}You'll definitely reap the rewards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right, we'll get rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone will be happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and everyone will get rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It really is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got this from my house; put it on the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's so beautiful... Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or should I say, it looks really expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Although this is my favorite decoration,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I couldn't put it on my own Christmas tree because it was too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll put it on carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Blackout curtains are okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The power source is okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, turn off the lights now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No one got hurt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was an accident, it couldn't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin, you're not at fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was just an unfortunate accident{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think it was because I spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I lost control of the ball and it broke something very important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I beg you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Although I might not be able to fix it, just let me do whatever I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then let Ryuuji hel{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.08,0:20:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No! Stop! Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun, just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me do this by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop it, it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you help me, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's not much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm not helping you, I'm just doing what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun... Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look, it's beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It can be fixed even if it's broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.09,0:21:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We can't put it back to how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it's still shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't even know if I can fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't worry, it can be fixed no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone, we're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're cuter than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have to come to the party tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll definitely be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:21:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't go after all the trouble I caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.24,0:22:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}because I won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.83,0:22:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.45,0:23:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Holy night! Holy night! Holy night! Holy night!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yay! It's a party on the holy night!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.12,0:23:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want more fruit punch!
